high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Pick up the bowl in the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bowl in the fridge and place it back in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left then cross the room head to the microwave
Open the microwave pick up the cup then close the microwave
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the cup then close the fridge
Turn right then head to the microwave
Open and put in the cup in the microwave then close it
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled cup in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the counter, turn right again and walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and take the wooden bowl out of the microwave, then close the microwave.
Walk over to the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and put the wooden bowl inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the chilled wooden bowl, then close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn right and walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and put the chilled wooden bowl inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wooden bowl in the microwave.
